{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1679-09_026","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"Le Veillard et l’Asne. Fable","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", septembre 1679 [tome 9], p. 26-31.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Vous m’avez paru assez contente de quelques Fables que je vous ay déja envoyées. En voicy une nouvelle qui ne vous déplaira pas. C'est la quinziéme du premier Livre de Phédre. Celuy qui s’est diverty à la traduire, est de Dijon. Elle a ce tour aisé &amp; naturel que vous avez remarqué dans tout ce que je vous ay fait voir de luy.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":[{"@type":"head","#1":{"value":"Le Veillard ","id":"/div/quote/label[0]/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"et l’Asne.","id":"/div/quote/label[0]/#2"}},{"@type":"head","#":{"value":"Fable.","id":"/div/quote/label[1]/#"}}],"l":[{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[0]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[0]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"UN timide Vieillard,","id":"/div/quote/l[0]/#"}},"Qui peut-estre en son temps ne fut que trop gaillard,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[2]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[2]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Passant pres d’un Village en Brie,","id":"/div/quote/l[2]/#"}},"(Brie, c’est pour rimer,) laissoit paistre à son gré",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[4]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[4]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Son Asne dans un Pré,","id":"/div/quote/l[4]/#"}},"Tandis que luy couché dessus l’herbe fleurie,","Dormoit tranquillement, &amp; ronfloit de bon cœur.",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[7]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[7]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Il dormit peu ; car par malheur","id":"/div/quote/l[7]/#"}},"Ayant eu toûjours l’ame assez mal aguerrie,","Il se sentit saisy tout-à-coup de frayeur,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[10]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[10]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Au bruit que faisoit le ravage","id":"/div/quote/l[10]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[11]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[11]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"De quelques Troupes de Soldats,","id":"/div/quote/l[11]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[12]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Qu'il vit de loin avancer à grands pas.","id":"/div/quote/l[12]/#"}},"Le bon Homme tremblant, se leve, &amp; prend courage.","Il exhorte son Asne à grands coups de baston,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[15]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[15]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"D'abandonner là le Chardon,","id":"/div/quote/l[15]/#"}},"Et de doubler le pas pour gagner le Village,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[17]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[17]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Craignant de tomber dans les mains","id":"/div/quote/l[17]/#"}},"De ces Soldats, Voleurs de grands Chemins.","Mais nostre Asne chargé de deux Sacs de Farine,","Allant toûjours son train, &amp; marchant gravement,","S'adressant au Vieillard, non sans faire la mine,",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[22]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[22]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Luy fit ce compliment.","id":"/div/quote/l[22]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si l’Ennemy sur nous enfin peut avoir prise","id":"/div/quote/l[23]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":",","id":"/div/quote/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon Maistre, dites-moy, croyez-vous franchement ","id":"/div/quote/l[24]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu'il me dust faire encor porter quelque Valise","id":"/div/quote/l[25]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":",","id":"/div/quote/l[25]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[26]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[26]/seg[1]/#"}}],"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou quelqu’autre nouveau Paquet","id":"/div/quote/l[26]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" ?","id":"/div/quote/l[26]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[27]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[27]/seg[1]/#"}}],"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non","id":"/div/quote/l[27]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":", répond l’Homme à barbe grise.","id":"/div/quote/l[27]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que m’importe-t-il donc","id":"/div/quote/l[28]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":", dit ce rusé Baudet,","id":"/div/quote/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À quel Maistre je sois, si comme à l’ordinaire ","id":"/div/quote/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je dois toûjours porter ma charge, &amp; qu’ay-je à faire ","id":"/div/quote/l[30]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/seg[1]/#"}}],"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De courir pour vous le galop","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" ?","id":"/div/quote/l[31]/#"}},"À vostre avis, cet Asne estoit-il sot ? pas trop.",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[33]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[33]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"La morale de cette Fable","id":"/div/quote/l[33]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[34]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"N'est souvent que trop véritable.","id":"/div/quote/l[34]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[35]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[35]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Quand dans les changemens d’Etat","id":"/div/quote/l[35]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[36]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/l[36]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"La misere devient commune,","id":"/div/quote/l[36]/#"}},"Le Riche y perd le plus, &amp; son destin s’abat ;","Mais celuy qui n’a rien, &amp; qui vit sans éclat,","Peut bien changer de Maistre, &amp; non pas de fortune."]}}}